sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayClient as Ray Client
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant WorkerPod as Ray Worker Pod<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant Operator as CodeFlare Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CertCtrl as cert-controller

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster OAuth Dashboard Access (OpenShift)
        User->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>No Auth (redirected to OAuth)
        Router->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (reencrypt)<br/>OpenShift OAuth token
        OAuthProxy->>Dashboard: HTTP/8265<br/>localhost (no encryption)<br/>Proxied (no auth)
        Dashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard Response
        OAuthProxy-->>Router: HTTPS Response
        Router-->>User: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over RayClient,HeadPod: Flow 2: RayClient mTLS Connection (OpenShift)
        RayClient->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS passthrough<br/>mTLS (per-cluster CA)
        Router->>HeadPod: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS<br/>Client cert (signed by cluster CA)
        HeadPod-->>Router: gRPC Response (mTLS)
        Router-->>RayClient: Response (TLS passthrough)
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over HeadPod,WorkerPod: Flow 3: Ray Head-Worker mTLS Communication
        HeadPod->>WorkerPod: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS<br/>Certs signed by per-cluster CA
        WorkerPod->>HeadPod: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS<br/>Certs signed by per-cluster CA
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Operator,CertCtrl: Operator Control Plane
        Operator->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>Watch RayCluster CRs
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayCluster events
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth Service,<br/>Route, SA, Secrets,<br/>NetworkPolicies
        CertCtrl->>K8sAPI: Rotate webhook TLS certs<br/>Patch webhook configs
    end
